if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係站入面放TG聽日返工既市民會唔會中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4e4634b4206c4d4dea2098c5943ed27072cc37","tid":1446932,"uid":189021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ccb640a7cc560119fffd283cede7fe4e0689af","tid":1446932,"uid":4948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ57Tr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=f0574932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ57Tr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=2b6ca47f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"1739b79ae9dfae9b68f40be340e201683d37feff","tid":1446932,"uid":130973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:07.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場"},{"pid":"8e2ff51e5d2719f744786da270a8a64e4a2b4774","tid":1446932,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"648af39e4d6d4484b1a1ad11b3884f09f5c8503d","tid":1446932,"uid":189021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b90d53a6c8dc04dc7ba97dc478fc6b7eafb7428","tid":1446932,"uid":144